## Scalability Considerations

### Current Limitations

```
Memory: Limited to session RAM
- ~5-10GB per instance typical
- Document size: <100MB recommended

Concurrency: Single-threaded
- One user per Gradio session
- Multiple instances for multiple users

Speed: API dependent
- Groq rate limits apply
- CPU/GPU hardware matters
```

### Scaling Options

```
Horizontal:
├─ Multiple Gradio instances
├─ Load balancer
└─ Shared document store

Vertical:
├─ Upgrade Hugging Face hardware
├─ Better GPU (A10G)
└─ More RAM

Database:
├─ Add PostgreSQL
├─ Vector DB for embeddings
└─ Cache layer
```

